    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551600/extras/93b9b481f46780492897b50216971d57.avif?t=1749284511\" width=616 height=72 /></span>当年轻的精灵骑士妮菲娅外出巡逻时，兽人们攻击了她的城堡，在城堡里烧杀抢掠。躲过了这一劫的妮菲娅发现形势并不乐观，因为兽人们这次还俘虏了许多队员，其中就包括精灵族的公主！事已至此，妮菲娅必须找到兽人们的老巢，和兽人们战斗并且尽快救出被俘虏的队员们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551600/extras/c6658be61f1d362873a78c835bcebaa8.avif?t=1749284511\" width=616 height=72 /></span>突破被敌人严防死守的地区，杀出一条血路吧！身为剑法与弓术的高手，妮菲娅既可以用剑将敌人斩于脚下，也可以用弓箭从远处射杀敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打败敌人后的战利品也相当丰厚——无论是宝石还是装备，亦或是可以用来强化妮菲娅的消耗品，道具总是多多益善。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551600/extras/1d0d006a803fb1a41dd9c26ea4823a71.avif?t=1749284511\" width=616 height=72 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551600/extras/29e3722545455e80f7c92a5670d4d7a6.avif?t=1749284511\" width=616 height=399 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551600/extras/435e74fb12ff9c8f1d2e5da78855b8d9.avif?t=1749284511\" width=616 height=72 /></span><strong>让角色随着剧情进度而成长</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏的过程中，您可以收集到神奇的利鲁娜草。它们不光可以增强妮菲娅的各项属性，有时还能让她习得全新的技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>各具特色的关卡</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏世界的大陆上旅行，并且在旅行的过程中访问各处独特的地点，品味不同的风土人情吧！</p>",
